short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Explore dive sights around the world each time you open a new tab

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Destination Tab is a fun Chrome extension that shows you different dive sites around the world every time you open a new browser tab, so that you can find inspiration for your next trip without wasting time on search.

Videos are submitted by divers and dive shops in our community.  Join us!
